Package: opentermix
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, qt6-svg-plugins
Description: Open-source lightweight MobaXterm-like terminal
 OpenTermix is an open-source, lightweight MobaXterm-like terminal
 for Linux. It provides tabbed embedded terminal (local shell and SSH),
 split view, multi-execution, SSH config editor, and a built-in SFTP
 file browser.
